commentTextItems.html: BANG and Zimbabwe takes the series 4 nil, tossed, on leg, Raza takes a few steps forward, crunches it over mid on for one bounce and over the rope

commentPostTextItems.html: Zimbabwe have won by 3 wickets to claim a 4 - 0 whitewash. The openers started like a house on fire cruising to 44 inside eight overs before Chari lost his wicket, then the next four wickets were lost for only 45 runs.
Maruma came in to save the sinking ship, smashed a 22 ball 35 with 3 fours and 2 sixes despite being dropped twice. Navved was peak of the bowlers with 2 for 26 in his 6 overs .
K Jarvis is the man of the match and R Chakabva is man of the series
Moor is getting the trophy and the rest of the team is coming to join him. That will be all from me Freeman Chigovera at Harare Sports Club. Cheers all. Congratulations Zimbabwe!
